text.tspan: We are a student run organization dedicated to
all things cyber security. We prepare teams to
compete in cyber security related competitions
and run weekly seminars for students of all
disciplines and levels. Are you interested in the
rapidly growing field of cyber security?
Join us weekly at the Watt Family Innovation
Center in room 316 every Thursday at 7:00pm!
Send us an email to get added to our mailing list!
